## Key Finding

Sunday service drops **{{ sunday_pct_drop|round(0)|int }}%** compared to weekday levels. **{{ n_sunday_desert|int|format_thousands }}** LSOAs ({{ pct_sunday_desert|round(1) }}%) have zero Sunday service — classified as "Sunday deserts" where residents have no public transport access on the day most frequently needed for leisure, healthcare, and family visits.

